<br>
Mistress Tebaun,<br>
<br>
I've grave news for you, and I'll not beat around with niceties.<br>
<br>
The body of Shintou Shinai was found washed ashore on an island in the Ocean of Tears this morning.  <br>
<br>
As he had no family to speak of, he was laid to rest privately.<br>
<br>
I know that you would have wanted to know from a source other than the gossip mill in Freeport, which is why I bade this brought to you with urgency.<br>
<br>
I know you feel loss, but know that he truly walks in Hate now.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Sarhea stared at the page for some minutes, with no reaction on her face. <br>
Finally, she crumpled to the floor, sobs wracking her halfelven frame.</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
